[I] Utility library for pattern matching of file paths

[T] utility library for pattern matching of file paths. So far this only
[T] includes Git’s wildmatch pattern matching which itself is derived
[T] from Rsync’s wildmatch. Git uses wildmatch for its gitignore files.

[U] https://pypi.org/project/pathspec/

